summary:
A former basketball player eager to work in a team, yet not afraid to take responsibility into my own hands and score. 

Branding and Trends in Consumer Marketing minor throughout an accelerated bachelor's program and hands-on experience in Digital Marketing assured me of my well-defined aspirations of becoming an asset for an international company that celebrates diversity and inclusion.

An exceptionally detail-oriented and determined individual passionate about the international environment and business studies, excited to grow professionally and personally with challenging opportunities ahead.
